Interface PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilderIetf

    public interface PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilder
extends PbMessageSubValueBuilder<PbMessageValueRemediationParameterString>
    Generic builder to build a TNCCS message string remediation parameter value compliant to RFC 5793. It can be used in a fluent way.
